<MainColumn title="Introduction">
  <p class="text-gray-500">
    Zerolines.js is a headless UI components for not writing any lines of
    JavaScript Code. You only need attaching behavior in your HTML element, then
    the element works as is.
  </p>
  <p>
    You don't need to prepare Simple JS script any more for common components
    such as Modal, Tab, Dropdown Menu, etc.
  </p>
</MainColumn>
